ZH: 他威胁着要揭发我的秘密。
EN: He threatened to expose my secret.

ZH: 这个公司的岗位威胁到小企业的生存。
EN: The positions in this company pose a threat to the survival of small businesses.

ZH: 在他发出威胁后，他得到了他想要的东西。
EN: After issuing the threat, he got what he wanted.

ZH: 他在电话中威胁着要伤害我。
EN: He threatened to hurt me over the phone.

ZH: 这场洪水威胁着整个社区的安全。
EN: The flood poses a threat to the safety of the entire community.

ZH: 如果你不乖乖交出钱来，我会威胁你的家人。
EN: If you don't hand over the money obediently, I will threaten your family.

ZH: 威胁已经消失了，你不需要再担心。
EN: The threat has disappeared, you don't need to worry anymore.

ZH: 这种病毒威胁着世界的健康。
EN: This virus threatens the health of the world.

ZH: 他扬言要威胁我的事业。
EN: He threatened to jeopardize my career.

ZH: 飓风威胁着沿海地区的人们。
EN: The hurricane threatens the people in the coastal areas.

ZH: 这个国家面临战争威胁。
EN: This country faces the threat of war.

ZH: 威胁利益的行为是不被容忍的。
EN: Actions that threaten interests are not tolerated.

ZH: 我不能容忍任何对我的家人的威胁。
EN: I cannot tolerate any threats against my family.

ZH: 他用暴力威胁着让我做一些不道德的事情。
EN: He used violence to threaten me into doing immoral things.

ZH: 这个政党一直被认为是国家安全的威胁。
EN: This political party has always been seen as a threat to national security.

ZH: 她威胁要离开他，除非他改变自己。
EN: She threatened to leave him unless he changed himself.

ZH: 这个恶势力团伙对整个社区带来了严重的威胁。
EN: This criminal gang poses a serious threat to the entire community.

ZH: 他威胁着要公开我曾经犯过的错误。
EN: He threatened to disclose the mistakes I had made in the past.

ZH: 在面对威胁时，我们必须保持冷静和镇定。
EN: In the face of threats, we must remain calm and composed.

ZH: 他曾经因为威胁他人而被起诉。
EN: He was once sued for threatening others.
